702
01:21:28,960 --> 01:21:30,518
D'you want me to?

703
01:21:32,160 --> 01:21:33,718
D'you want me to?

704
01:21:34,080 --> 01:21:35,638
I do!

705
01:22:26,880 --> 01:22:28,438
Don't worry,

706
01:22:29,440 --> 01:22:31,317
