official people.

754
01:27:57,120 --> 01:27:58,348
Of course.

755
01:27:59,040 --> 01:28:02,191
Will Ondris meet the train?

756
01:28:03,840 --> 01:28:05,068
Sure to.

757
01:28:08,640 --> 01:28:09,868
Well then,

758
01:28:10,240 --> 01:28:11,468
take care.

759
01:29:09,440 --> 01:29:10,668
